      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Preformatted forms on which a consumer may indicate a required product or service. This form is subsequently consulted by the supplier of the product or service.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
